336
00:14:19,680 --> 00:14:20,680
You know what?
你知道吗？

337
00:14:20,680 --> 00:14:30,400
I'll just have everything dry cleaned.
我还是把所有东西都送去干洗吧。

338
00:14:30,400 --> 00:14:32,080
Have you ever had any laundry mishaps?
你洗衣服时出过什么意外吗？

339
00:14:32,080 --> 00:14:35,720
Have you ever lost a sock, dyed something?
你丢过袜子，或者把衣服染过色吗？

340
00:14:35,720 --> 00:14:37,240
Have I ever.
当然有过。

341
00:14:37,240 --> 00:14:39,800
I hate doing the laundry.
我讨厌洗衣服。

342
00:14:39,800 --> 00:14:40,800
Why?
为什么？

343
00:14:40,800 --> 00:14:41,800
So much.
太讨厌了。

344
00:14:41,800 --> 00:14:42,800
It's time consuming.
太费时间了。

345
00:14:42,800 --> 00:14:46,600
It takes a lot of time and I just have no patience.
它花很多时间，而且我根本没耐心。

346
00:14:46,600 --> 00:14:51,560
And so normally, when I was in college, I would take all of my laundry in a bag and
所以通常，我上大学的时候，会把所有衣服装进一个袋子，

347
00:14:51,560 --> 00:14:55,040
I'd throw it in the washing machine and I'd put it on cold.
扔进洗衣机，然后设定冷水洗。

348
00:14:55,040 --> 00:15:00,040
Because cold water, it's okay for all colors, but hot water makes the colors bleed.
因为冷水对所有颜色都安全，但热水会让颜色褪色。

349
00:15:00,040 --> 00:15:04,320
I took out the clothes and put them in the dryer and afterwards I saw all my clothes
我把衣服拿出来放进烘干机，之后发现所有衣服

350
00:15:04,320 --> 00:15:08,480
were clean except for my three sweaters, which were small enough for babies.
都干净了，除了三件毛衣，它们小到婴儿都能穿。

351
00:15:08,480 --> 00:15:10,480
Oh, you shrunk it.
哦，你把它们洗缩水了。

352
00:15:10,480 --> 00:15:15,520
I shrunk three brand new sweaters.
我把三件新毛衣洗缩水了。

353
00:15:15,520 --> 00:15:20,720
The problem that I have when doing laundry is that I forget that I started doing laundry.
我洗衣服时的问题是，我忘了自己开始洗衣服了。

354
00:15:20,720 --> 00:15:26,200
So all of a sudden, I'm doing laundry in the morning and then clothes are washed, but they're
所以突然之间，我早上洗衣服，衣服洗好了，但

355
00:15:26,200 --> 00:15:27,480
still in the washing machine.
还留在洗衣机里。

356
00:15:27,480 --> 00:15:29,280
And I remember the next day.
然后我第二天才想起来。

357
00:15:29,280 --> 00:15:32,480
So then the clothes are smelling kind of humid.
所以衣服闻起来有点潮。

358
00:15:32,480 --> 00:15:34,480
Because they're moldy.
因为它们发霉了。

359
00:15:34,480 --> 00:15:37,760
So I have to rewash them and it's just a pain.
所以我得重新洗，真是麻烦。

360
00:15:37,760 --> 00:15:41,920
And doing laundry is sometimes so time consuming, but let us know what you think.
洗衣服有时很费时间，但让我们知道你的想法。

361
00:15:41,920 --> 00:15:45,280
Do you like doing laundry or have you ever lost a sock?
你喜欢洗衣服吗，或者有没有丢过袜子？

362
00:15:45,280 --> 00:15:48,960
I think everyone has lost a sock or something in the washing, right?
我想每个人都丢过袜子之类的东西在洗衣机里，对吧？

363
00:15:48,960 --> 00:15:49,960
I don't know what happens.
我也不知道怎么回事。

364
00:15:49,960 --> 00:15:52,320
I think there's a secret home for socks somewhere.
我觉得袜子有个秘密的家在某个地方。

365
00:15:52,320 --> 00:15:53,480
It's so weird.
真是太奇怪了。

366
00:15:53,480 --> 00:15:55,760
Maybe it's in Australia or something.
也许在澳大利亚之类的地方。

367
00:15:55,760 --> 00:15:58,800
So come to our website, EnglishPod.com.
所以来我们的网站 EnglishPod.com 吧。

368
00:15:58,800 --> 00:16:02,500
Give us all your feedback, questions, comments or suggestions.
给我们所有的反馈、问题、评论或建议。

369
00:16:02,500 --> 00:16:03,500
And we're always there.
我们一直都在那里。

370
00:16:03,500 --> 00:16:04,500
All right.
好的。

371
00:16:04,500 --> 00:16:05,500
Hope to hear from you soon.
希望很快收到你的消息。

372
00:16:05,500 --> 00:16:06,500
And until next time, everyone.
下次再见，各位。

373
00:16:06,500 --> 00:16:07,500
Bye.
拜拜。

374
00:16:07,500 --> 00:16:08,000
Bye.
拜拜。
